{
  "title": "Magnificently Melty Peruvian Natto Rocoto Relleno",
  "description": "A show-stopping Peruvian dish featuring natto, with a melty cheese pull, served in a tagine pot, perfect for a special occasion dinner",
  "cuisine": "Peruvian",
